1003
01:11:03.225 --> 01:11:05.102
God, I want him back.

1004
01:11:11.900 --> 01:11:14.361
I'll be here if you need me, okay?

1005
01:13:07.558 --> 01:13:10.144
God, he loved flying with you, Maverick.

1006
01:13:28.412 --> 01:13:30.372
